data.name: ParseResult
desc: Parser results returned by XCharacterClassification.parseAnyToken() and XCharacterClassification.parsePredefinedToken().

items.name: CharLen
lines: Number of code points (not UTF-16 code units) of the parsed token, not including leading whitespace.

items.name: ContFlags
lines: KParseTokens flags of remaining characters of actual token matched.

items.name: DequotedNameOrString
lines: If a quoted name or string is encountered the dequoted result goes here.

items.name: EndPos
lines: UTF-16 code unit index of first unprocessed character.

items.name: LeadingWhiteSpace
lines: Count of ignored leading whitespace, in UTF-16 code units, not Unicode code points.

items.name: StartFlags
lines: KParseTokens flags of first character of actual token matched.
If TokenType is a KParseType.SINGLE_QUOTE_NAME or a KParseType.DOUBLE_QUOTE_STRING the first character is the first character inside the quotes, not the quote itself.

items.name: Value
lines: Value of token in case of numeric.
